'''Daniel Hotz''' is a [[Switzerland|Swiss]] [[orienteering]] [[Competition|competitor]] and World champion.<ref name="woc">[http://old.orientering.no/resultater/vmres.asp World Orienteering Championship, senior statistics 1966-2006] <small>(Retrieved on January 26, 2008)</small></ref> He won a gold medal at the 1995 [[World Orienteering Championships]] in [[Detmold]] with the Swiss relay team ([[Alain Berger]], [[Christian Aebersold]] and [[Urs Fl<U+00FC>hmann]]).

